  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You gain the following benefits for your Hunter Class Features.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Hunter’s Mark</span></strong></span></p><p>The Help die granted by Hunter’s Mark is increased to a d10 and the first Martial Attack against your target on your turn ignores Physical Resistance.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Favored Terrain</span></strong></span></p><p>You gain 1 additional Favored Terrain.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Hunter’s Strike</span></strong></span></p><p>You can use up to 2 Hunter’s Strike Enhancements on an Attack.</p>",
